This build needs the opencv sumodule to be built correctly :
    Linux :
        Build as static lib
        Disable IPP
        Install localy in opencv/install/
    Win32 :
        Build as dynamic lib
        Install localy in opencv/install/

To deploy the windows executable :
    Copy dependant opencv dlls
    Copy the content of lib_for_windows
    Copy the executable


